 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We describe simple didactic experiments on radiation detection and statistics counts using the Arduino platform for application in secondary and higher education. The experiments illustrate the binominal nature of the radioactive decay process. The setup enables the students to measure the distributions of Poisson and Gauss.</subfield>
